  "text": "Yeah, man. Behind the bank. Ball guy. Billionaire. Right in the TD bank. Right here? Yep. Excuse me, sir. Sir, how old were you when you became a millionaire? Who are you guys? I've reached over 18 million followers. I've interviewed 31 billionaires in the last four years. I've seen you on Instagram. Yes, sir. And they know I am. The cops over there, they told me that you're a billionaire. Did they tell you that? Yeah, they did. That's how you need to ask me questions. Yeah, yeah, that's how I do it. By the way, thank God for the filthy police department. They do a phenomenal job. What line of business are you in? I'm an entrepreneur. But if you turn around, I own from this corner to the next corner. So you owed all these buildings over here. How in the world did you get money to be able to buy buildings like that? I had friendly banks. So you got along well with the bank? You know what? I also paid back the banks, so they saw me as a good client and a good customer. So how much equity would you put into these properties? Would it be like a 30, 70 sort of split between you and the bank? Typically it was 30% down. A lot of times I had to leverage by other real estate and sign off to get the equity. Did you ever think growing up that this was going to be possible, that you were going to own the entire block here in downtown Philadelphia? My real goal is to build a tremendous community here in Philadelphia. And my only reason for wanting to buy these properties was to put in great tenants that people would love to go to. Because I think at the end of the day, as my father taught me, he said, we grow old too soon and wise too late. And what I wanted to do was create an environment that was a lot of fun. How old are you now? I'm not telling you. Give me your age. Give me an idea. You can guess. I'll take it. I have to go. What's your name? Alan. If me and you died tomorrow and you had one more message to leave with the younger generation, what would that be? Spend as much time as you can with your family. Yeah. Do you have any regrets? No regrets. But when I was 40, my brother was 44 and he passed away. My only sibling. So I miss him. Thank you so much for your time. So I appreciate you. Do you believe in God? Yeah. Has faith helped you out? Yes. What got you through that? You're a good interviewer. Did you enjoy it? Yeah. Yeah? He's very good. Yeah. What got you through that? I think whatever religion you are, praying to God, but also taking care of family. I love that. Could I get your contact? Yeah.",
  "segments": [
    {
      "start": 0.4,
      "end": 1.1,
      "text": "Yeah, man."
    },
    {
      "start": 1.4,
      "end": 1.9,
      "text": "Behind the bank."
    },
    {
      "start": 2.1,
      "end": 2.6,
      "text": "Ball guy."
    },
    {
      "start": 3.0,
      "end": 3.3,
      "text": "Billionaire."
    },
    {
      "start": 3.7,
      "end": 4.6,
      "text": "Right in the TD bank."
    },
    {
      "start": 4.6,
      "end": 4.9,
      "text": "Right here?"
    },
    {
      "start": 5.3,
      "end": 5.4,
      "text": "Yep."
    },
    {
      "start": 5.6,
      "end": 6.2,
      "text": "Excuse me, sir."
    },
    {
      "start": 6.6,
      "end": 9.3,
      "text": "Sir, how old were you when you became a millionaire?"
    },
    {
      "start": 9.8,
      "end": 10.3,
      "text": "Who are you guys?"
    },
    {
      "start": 10.5,
      "end": 12.1,
      "text": "I've reached over 18 million followers."
    },
    {
      "start": 12.3,
      "end": 14.0,
      "text": "I've interviewed 31 billionaires in the last four years."
    },
    {
      "start": 14.1,
      "end": 14.9,
      "text": "I've seen you on Instagram."
    },
    {
      "start": 15.2,
      "end": 15.6,
      "text": "Yes, sir."
    },
    {
      "start": 15.8,
      "end": 16.4,
      "text": "And they know I am."
    },
    {
      "start": 16.5,
      "end": 18.2,
      "text": "The cops over there, they told me that you're a billionaire."
    },
    {
      "start": 18.4,
      "end": 18.9,
      "text": "Did they tell you that?"
    },
    {
      "start": 19.0,
      "end": 19.4,
      "text": "Yeah, they did."
    },
    {
      "start": 19.6,
      "end": 20.8,
      "text": "That's how you need to ask me questions."
    },
    {
      "start": 21.1,
      "end": 22.0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah, that's how I do it."
    },
    {
      "start": 22.0,
      "end": 24.2,
      "text": "By the way, thank God for the filthy police department."
    },
    {
      "start": 24.3,
      "end": 25.6,
      "text": "They do a phenomenal job."
    },
    {
      "start": 25.7,
      "end": 26.6,
      "text": "What line of business are you in?"
    },
    {
      "start": 26.7,
      "end": 27.5,
      "text": "I'm an entrepreneur."
    },
    {
      "start": 27.5,
      "end": 30.6,
      "text": "But if you turn around, I own from this corner to the next corner."
    },
    {
      "start": 30.9,
      "end": 32.3,
      "text": "So you owed all these buildings over here."
    },
    {
      "start": 32.4,
      "end": 35.0,
      "text": "How in the world did you get money to be able to buy buildings like that?"
    },
    {
      "start": 35.1,
      "end": 35.8,
      "text": "I had friendly banks."
    },
    {
      "start": 36.2,
      "end": 37.2,
      "text": "So you got along well with the bank?"
    },
    {
      "start": 37.4,
      "end": 37.7,
      "text": "You know what?"
    },
    {
      "start": 37.8,
      "end": 41.1,
      "text": "I also paid back the banks, so they saw me as a good client and a good customer."
    },
    {
      "start": 41.3,
      "end": 43.3,
      "text": "So how much equity would you put into these properties?"
    },
    {
      "start": 43.4,
      "end": 45.7,
      "text": "Would it be like a 30, 70 sort of split between you and the bank?"
    },
    {
      "start": 45.9,
      "end": 47.5,
      "text": "Typically it was 30% down."
    },
    {
      "start": 47.7,
      "end": 51.2,
      "text": "A lot of times I had to leverage by other real estate and sign off to get the equity."
    },
    {
      "start": 51.4,
      "end": 53.3,
      "text": "Did you ever think growing up that this was going to be possible,"
    },
    {
      "start": 53.4,
      "end": 55.8,
      "text": "that you were going to own the entire block here in downtown Philadelphia?"
    },
    {
      "start": 55.8,
      "end": 59.4,
      "text": "My real goal is to build a tremendous community here in Philadelphia."
    },
    {
      "start": 59.8,
      "end": 62.8,
      "text": "And my only reason for wanting to buy these properties was to put in great tenants"
    },
    {
      "start": 62.8,
      "end": 64.2,
      "text": "that people would love to go to."
    },
    {
      "start": 64.4,
      "end": 66.4,
      "text": "Because I think at the end of the day, as my father taught me,"
    },
    {
      "start": 66.4,
      "end": 69.1,
      "text": "he said, we grow old too soon and wise too late."
    },
    {
      "start": 69.2,
      "end": 71.5,
      "text": "And what I wanted to do was create an environment that was a lot of fun."
    },
    {
      "start": 71.7,
      "end": 72.2,
      "text": "How old are you now?"
    },
    {
      "start": 72.4,
      "end": 73.0,
      "text": "I'm not telling you."
    },
    {
      "start": 73.4,
      "end": 74.1,
      "text": "Give me your age."
    },
    {
      "start": 74.2,
      "end": 74.6,
      "text": "Give me an idea."
    },
    {
      "start": 74.7,
      "end": 75.1,
      "text": "You can guess."
    },
    {
      "start": 75.8,
      "end": 76.5,
      "text": "I'll take it."
    },
    {
      "start": 76.6,
      "end": 77.0,
      "text": "I have to go."
    },
    {
      "start": 77.2,
      "end": 78.2,
      "text": "What's your name?"
    },
    {
      "start": 78.6,
      "end": 78.9,
      "text": "Alan."
    },
    {
      "start": 79.1,
      "end": 82.7,
      "text": "If me and you died tomorrow and you had one more message to leave with the younger generation,"
    },
    {
      "start": 82.8,
      "end": 83.4,
      "text": "what would that be?"
    },
    {
      "start": 83.8,
      "end": 86.0,
      "text": "Spend as much time as you can with your family."
    },
    {
      "start": 86.4,
      "end": 86.7,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 87.0,
      "end": 87.7,
      "text": "Do you have any regrets?"
    },
    {
      "start": 88.3,
      "end": 88.8,
      "text": "No regrets."
    },
    {
      "start": 89.0,
      "end": 93.5,
      "text": "But when I was 40, my brother was 44 and he passed away."
    },
    {
      "start": 93.8,
      "end": 94.4,
      "text": "My only sibling."
    },
    {
      "start": 94.8,
      "end": 95.5,
      "text": "So I miss him."
    },
    {
      "start": 95.8,
      "end": 96.6,
      "text": "Thank you so much for your time."
    },
    {
      "start": 96.7,
      "end": 97.4,
      "text": "So I appreciate you."
    },
    {
      "start": 97.4,
      "end": 98.0,
      "text": "Do you believe in God?"
    },
    {
      "start": 98.3,
      "end": 98.5,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 98.7,
      "end": 99.4,
      "text": "Has faith helped you out?"
    },
    {
      "start": 99.8,
      "end": 99.9,
      "text": "Yes."
    },
    {
      "start": 100.2,
      "end": 101.0,
      "text": "What got you through that?"
    },
    {
      "start": 101.1,
      "end": 102.0,
      "text": "You're a good interviewer."
    },
    {
      "start": 102.2,
      "end": 102.8,
      "text": "Did you enjoy it?"
    },
    {
      "start": 102.9,
      "end": 103.0,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 103.4,
      "end": 103.7,
      "text": "Yeah?"
    },
    {
      "start": 104.1,
      "end": 104.6,
      "text": "He's very good."
    },
    {
      "start": 104.8,
      "end": 105.0,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 105.1,
      "end": 106.0,
      "text": "What got you through that?"
    },
    {
      "start": 106.1,
      "end": 108.0,
      "text": "I think whatever religion you are, praying to God,"
    },
    {
      "start": 108.3,
      "end": 109.6,
      "text": "but also taking care of family."
    },
    {
      "start": 109.9,
      "end": 110.3,
      "text": "I love that."
    },
    {
      "start": 110.3,
      "end": 111.0,
      "text": "Could I get your contact?"
    },
    {
      "start": 111.4,
